{
  "text": "3.5.1.1. Construction phase assessment. The first step is to acquire relevant cost data for the evaluation of the different options [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The focus of the LCC analysis was to compare different heating energy solutions for the development (excluding residents' energy demand for household electricity). For all the defined investment options (Section 3.3), cost data was attained from the cost estimators of the construction company and a photovoltaic panel supplier.",
